Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:02.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Success! Integrity! Evidence and its impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.95,0:00:04.62,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An endless drive to become the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:06.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The year gets off to an unwelcome start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.29,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A case turns up as Ran gets a heart-shocking love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:10.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:12.62,Narration Off,,10,10,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.51,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear? Kitada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} from Class C got dumped again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran! Going home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sonoko! Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:14.94,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,I was thinking about cooking something good for Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. He hasn't been eating any dinner lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beautiful young schoolgirl like you shouldn't be thinking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki, you could learn something from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll head home too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get my bag, so wait for me by the shoe lockers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:46.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:56.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'd better open it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To Ran Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S.H.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Ran, it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it in my shoes locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just rip it open already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Please forgive me for sending you this letter so suddenly.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:43.42,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,'Whenever I'm thinking about you, Ran-{\i1}sempai{\i0}, I can feel my heart beating. I can't even sleep at night.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I would like to meet you.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I'll be waiting for you tomorrow after school, at the fountain in Beika Park.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congrats, Ran! It's a love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he called you 'Ran-{\i1}sempai{\i0}', he has to be a first-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know you already have Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with Shin'ichi—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't even have a simple conversation here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you got a love letter?\NI haven't had any in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, it's the first time you got one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always with Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, so nobody sends you any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you this has nothing to do with Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he a former {\i1}kendō{\i0} club member?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, he's holding a {\i1}shinai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But never mind that, focus on the love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll go, right? To Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'll do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to think about!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll go and turn him down in a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll say you already have a husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't act like it's somebody else's problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}do{\i0} look worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess there's no choice. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll turn him down for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to turn down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's four-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look weird, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! She got her very first love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Oh, my beloved Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:42.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I'll hold you close and place a loving kiss on your sweet lips...'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's lying, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't say anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you really {\i1}did{\i0} get a love letter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're interested, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid, why would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I {\i1}am{\i0} a bit interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a first-year student with the initials 'S. H.'.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:04.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A first-year student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to meet her tomorrow at the fountain in Beika Park after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran doesn't know how to handle it, so I'm going to go and turn him down instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:22.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez. And I can't do anything. Who could've sent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What should I do? Can I really\Njust leave it to Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's mine if he's handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something's bothering you, you can talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her father's the great detective Kogorō Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her husband's the high school detective Shin'ichi Kudō.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know Detective Mouri, and the high-school detective Kudō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to be a Teitan High student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're second-year students.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should talk about it with you, like that boy suggested...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can, right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you don't mind speaking to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll help you, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in! Sorry for the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died one year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stayed in the hospital for six months and fought hard, but he couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, it seems someone broke into my house while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went for a walk with Yūto for two hours at around 1 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I must've forgotten to lock that window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I usually personally hand the rent to the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I withdrew some money from the bank this morning and put it in this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it seems the money I had in here was taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taken out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was put back. All the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how do you know it was taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because the money was folded even though you got new notes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly. It's a very faint fold though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I always leave my diary here too, but it looks like someone's been reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The best proof is that someone burnt an incense stick there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was still burning when you arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much of the stick was left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was about half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:09:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the incense stick was lit about 15 minutes before you got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, incense sticks usually last about half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know a lot, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This brat always knows strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone really broke into this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is who broke in and why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He read the diary, so isn't he a stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But except for that diary, it didn't look like anything had been looked through or taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though a thief wouldn't bring the money back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's hard to imagine a thief lighting up an incense stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt a little bit uncomfortable, so I asked a policeman to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but since nothing was taken,\Nthere wasn't anything to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The incense stick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's the most intriguing part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:52.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is the culprit one of her acquaintances, or one of her husband's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, how did you meet your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's really a curious brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a classmate of mine in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we had no feelings for each other back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After graduating from university, we happened to meet each other in the city and started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's not like Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, you said someone read your diary, but what was written in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things like 'working and taking care of a child everyday is tough,'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'but I get some strength when I think about him.' Childish stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be really hard being alone, Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I already thought about committing suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have a child, and thought about my late husband who struggled so hard with his illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it's not just my husband. There are so many people who want to live but can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it'd be unforgivable for me to give up my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's so sad, I'm shedding tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:14.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe the culprit felt the same way we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If that's true, our culprit would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:27.52,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,Hey, I saw on TV that a thief broke into a house and left without stealing anything after changing his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was the house of a teacher who'd been kind to him when he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he broke in without knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, you wouldn't happen to be a school teacher, would—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if you weren't their teacher, you could be somebody they know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More to the point, you could be somebody special to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should write a diary, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they read said special person's diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A diary that shows so clearly that you're living honestly despite many misfortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! That's why they didn't take anything and instead just lit an incense stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:05.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he even sent you a love letter during high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop joking, Sonoko! We're being serious here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm serious too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I {\i1}did{\i0} get a love letter once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The January of my third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if it hadn't been for that letter,\NI wouldn't even know his name or face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd never been in the same class at all, from first year to third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But apparently he'd always been admiring me, and I just didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The king of one-sided love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The letter said he wanted to meet me at the fountain in Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:13:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hesitated, but I went to tell him my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I'm glad you have those feelings for me,'
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'but I can't think of anything other than the entrance exams right now.'
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing that, he just left without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shūhei Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! This man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, were you part of the {\i1}kendō{\i0} club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was the manager during my 2nd year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought. That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, he's the one who broke into your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:02.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, have you heard from him since you graduated?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, about two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From one of my husband's friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never spoke about him to my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he came up in conversation as one of the many other classmates we had at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:25.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He did his best, but he couldn't enter the university he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:29.24,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And after graduating, he only found a job in a company he didn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:33.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the end, he quit that company, and it seems he's doing part-time jobs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, by any chance did you enter a top university just after high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'd call it a top university, but I {\i1}did{\i0} enter the university I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it. I saw through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to hear my deduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:55.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh geez, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:15:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After meeting Yuriko-{\i1}sempai{\i0} at the Beika Park fountain, Shūhei Nagai didn't forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But feeling inferior to her, who'd entered a top university just after high-school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he couldn't bring himself to contact her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, after graduation, as his professional life wasn't any good either,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he ended up without money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As he was already familiar with Beika District, he chose it to commit his theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he was headed to a rich mansion, probably mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and on the way there, he noticed the window in your house was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He figured out the house was empty, and he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The woman in the photo was the one he'd fallen in love with in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also remembered the man with her as a high school classmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And from the picture on the altar, he realised that the classmate in question had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while he knew it was wrong, he also read the diary he'd found.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He found out about how you were doing your best to live on with your son,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and thought about his classmate who died in his 20s.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:18.30,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,So he started feeling ashamed of himself, as he was taking advantage of people despite still being healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I see Ran put so much effort into her karate practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sometimes think I should work hard too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Shūhei Nagai decided to redeem himself, and so he put the money back in the envelope,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,burnt a stick in honour of his late classmate, and left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, as he knew he would never come back to this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he went to see the school he graduated from one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that just happened to be when the {\i1}kendō{\i0} club was practising.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, he remembered Yuriko-{\i1}sempai{\i0} and started reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might be staring at the fountain in Beika Park now even!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was almost the same as what I deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This Nagai guy who I saw in front of the gymnasium seemed a little bit different than you deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked rather languished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I still don't know why he was carrying a {\i1}shinai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A {\i1}shinai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, was there anything else written in the diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's actually something I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About 10 days ago, I was involved in a small accident with a man riding a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, he said everything was OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he came back later saying he couldn't turn his head any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told him that I'd pay for his medical fees,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he asked for a 'relationship' instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite persistently, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:19.34,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,He seemed like a pretty bad guy, so I was afraid something might happen to my son if I'd rejected him too harshly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I didn't tell anybody about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was he today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's on a business trip until tonight, and I don't think he was today's intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, everything you just told us was written in your diary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this Nagai guy was carrying a {\i1}shinai{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you that girl's boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:19:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And keep your hands off her kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What are you blabbering?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had enough yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you sayin'? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you couldn't turn your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You despicable monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister, it seems you can't turn your neck for real now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I read your diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,11 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,11 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so glad you'd come to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind. I'll go there by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:21:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what I'll say, but I have to tell him how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I owe him my sincerity for having written that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.77,0:22:50.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:55.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:23:00.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran said she wanted to tell him the truth, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:03.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did she mean about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I'd wait for you, but you ended up being the one waiting for me, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:17.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.23,0:23:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a big fan of you, Ran-{\i1}sempai{\i0}, the captain of the karate club!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thanks.{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep doing your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a first-year boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko! And Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here I thought I was gonna hear Ran's true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're able to grasp women's hearts too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.50,0:23:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.01,0:23:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A girl who looks like Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did she get involved in some sort of case?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan:\N'The Super-Secret Path to School (Part I)'!
