Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:24.00,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2\fad(150,200)}Looking only for the truth, I tremble every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:31.46,ShoudouTL,,1,11,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2\fad(149,0)}Though what's inside my tough façade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:34.30,ShoudouTL,,1,11,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}is a mystery even to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.93,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}(the blazes of freedom)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:42.27,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}Only through forging steel-like bonds with others
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:48.02,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}can I repair my own dented heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:53.69,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}'You do know that even you can change things?'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:59.20,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}Please, casually whisper that in my ear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:04.96,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}As it's your voice that drives me to see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:10.60,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2\fsp-0.5}'You do know that even you can give someone love?'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:16.13,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}I want you to take my hands and tell me so
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:21.76,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}Hope is the road leading forward in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:27.40,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}so let's believe that it must lead somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:33.40,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}Everything about you drives me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:36.18,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}Go for it! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:38.99,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}Love itself is impulsive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:41.82,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2}Go for it! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:45.32,ShoudouTL,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.25\blur2\fad(0,500)}Love itself is impulsive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:31.40,EDTLKanashii,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I never realised before, but I miss you so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:39.82,EDTLKanashii,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}There's so much sad news in this city
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:46.22,EDTLKanashii,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}On days when I don't hear from you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:55.55,EDTLKanashii,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}everything about me stands still
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:22:01.44,EDTLKanashii,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I love you so much that it brings me to tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:11.52,EDTLKanashii,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I wonder why I yearn for you so much? Why is it so painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.52,0:22:20.36,EDTLKanashii,,10,10,0,,{\blur2\fsp-0.4}I have to take my courage and throw open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:25.66,EDTLKanashii,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}as you filled my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:30.02,EDTLKanashii,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}with all the colours of the sunrise...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:35.68,EDTLKanashii,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,200)}So I will make it with you
